{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"To increase the chance of placing high-priority labels on the map, you can"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"provide an array of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textAnchor"},{"text":" locations, each paired with an offset value.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"The renderer will attempt to place the label at each location, in order, before","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"moving on to the next location+offset. Use "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textJustify: auto"},{"text":" to choose","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"justification based on anchor position.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSExpression","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSExpression","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"textVariableAnchorOffset"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The length of the array must be even, and must alternate between enum and","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"point entries. i.e., each anchor location must be accompanied by a point, and","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"that point defines the offset when the corresponding anchor location is used."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Positive offset values indicate right and down, while negative values indicate","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"left and up. Anchor locations may repeat, allowing the renderer to try multiple","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"offsets to try and place a label using the sa